<br>
the biggest help in my learning to quad was learning to play in 3rd person view.  this helps a great deal in pulling mobs with the tflux, and with avoiding adds.<br>
<br>
to switch to 3rd person view, i hit F9 3 times, and then hold down alt+delete, and then alt+up arrow, to back up the view as far as possible.  when needing to loot, or run back to a specific med spot, i hit F9 twice to return to first person view.<br>
